  Kinetic (Delta T^0):                   0.651126203837545         17.7180           408.59          1709.53
  Delta V^Pauli Coulomb:                -0.392625854019824        -10.6839          -246.38         -1030.84
  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -0.156299660868649         -4.2531           -98.08          -410.36
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.046692429650943          1.2706            29.30           122.59
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Correlation:        -0.025690112073254         -0.6991           -16.12           -67.45
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
  Total Pauli Repulsion:                 0.123203006526761          3.3525            77.31           323.47
 (Total Pauli Repulsion =
  Delta E^Pauli in BB paper)

